1. fargate-task-execution -> Role ( + giving ECS permission to assume this role ) + Policy
        A. Create a role for the task execution role having a trust policy
                aws iam create-role `
                --role-name XpressBuy-Service-Execution-Role `
                --assume-role-policy-document file://C:/Users/.../service-assume-role-execution-policy.json


        B. Make a new policy and attach it to the role
                aws iam put-role-policy `
                --policy-name XpressBuy-Service-Execution-Policy `
                --role-name XpressBuy-Service-Execution-Role `
                --policy-document file://C:/Users/.../service-execution-policy.json




// 2. fargate-task-execution -> Task Role ( + giving ECS permission to assume this role ) + Policy